title: BACK TO SCHOOL: PUSH YOURSELF
itunes:title: BACK TO SCHOOL: PUSH YOURSELF
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
MAKE THIS SCHOOL YEAR YOUR BEST ONE YET! As back to school rolls out around the world, we're revisiting some of our most motivational speeches to get you motivated for the upcoming year.


Push Yourself!! This is a powerful Motivational Speech on how you have MASSIVE Potential, but success isn't going to come easy! You have to give it everything you've got!


Speaker:


Freddy Fri


Freddy Fri inspires people to “win the day so that they can win in life." Subscribe today and join the Winner's Circle!


Subscribe to Freddy: http://bit.ly/FreddyFri


Request Freddy to speak at your next event: http://www.freddyfri.com/hire-me


Music:


Immediate Music - Of Gods and Men


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
